Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The death toll is at 5\Nwith 34 injured in the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Fredrich Emmanuel Library\Nat Munich University.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A grueling search\Nfor the missing is still underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a chance to speak with\Nsome of the survivors. Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew what was happening,\Nwe were surrounded by flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The place was filled with smoke\Nand I couldn't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A man saved us. He was an Asian man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He shot the door hinges\Nwith his gun and opened the door for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for him,\Na lot more people would have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have determined
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that this fire was deliberately set\Nwith kerosene and gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They've announced that they're doing\Neverything possible to find the arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been burned to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess all this human wisdom doesn't\Namount to much when it's all burned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Any fingerprints on\Nthe sniper rifle that was found?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we'll find any\Nafter it's been through this fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is definitely a Mauser SR93,\Njust like the one bought by
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the Japanese man thought to be Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After a fire like this, it's unlikely\Nwe'll find a trace of the arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every crime scene has evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a cufflink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a human around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who can be somewhere without leaving\Na trace of their presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If they can do that,\Nthen they're not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But if by chance they didn't leave\Nany trace, then what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But those don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, anyone who commits\Na crime can be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I speak with Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in intensive care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His burns weren't that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but considering his age,\Nthey've decided not to allow visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's talk to him.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let you see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's conscious, right?\NWe'll be through in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Schuwald is in\Nan extreme state of shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He must rest for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about\Nwhat happened to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lunge from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I told the police earlier\Nthat there was someone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man\Nwho tried to assassinate your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You honestly don't know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't. But he might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to find Johan Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan was also\Nat the ceremony with my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't find him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NWe'll start searching for him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place\Nthat Johan Liebert was renting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He moved out about two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no record of him\Nat the law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't really a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you contacted his parents\Nwho live in Offenbach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a dead end as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They are almost rarely spoke\Nwith neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want us to dust this place\Nfor fingerprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-I doubt you'll find any.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No record of his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This place feels as if\Nnobody has ever lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you weren't\Nseriously injured, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry\Nabout me, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You better believe I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept pulling people out of there,\Nbut you never came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so afraid for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With those injuries, I'm surprised\Nyou made it out of that fire on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The firemen were surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone helped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the last person\Nto come out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A Japanese man…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't a Japanese doctor\Ntaken to one of the hospitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There were several Japanese people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think they were all businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I was trapped\Nbeneath a curtain when he found me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Attendees of the ceremony reported that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,just before the fire,\Nyou told everyone to evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have realized something\Nwas about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mr. Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's about enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it if I hold it this close?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This man attempted to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Some witnesses say he was at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,According to witnesses,\Nthey say that this man saved people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. I'm putting an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If he remembers anything,\Ncall me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the whereabouts of\Nyour secretary, Johan Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone completely senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After going through something like that\Nat his age, it's no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is the end of the road\Nfor the financial kingpin,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the Vampire of Bavaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, it's not.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell from his eyes\Nthat he understood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk to some of the other witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a list of the victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is going on anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, witnesses said that someone\Nwho looks like Tenma rescued people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it could be\Na case of multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nina"…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nina Fortner."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that name ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina Fortner was released this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The address on the police record was fake.\NWhat's in the hospital records?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. I'll look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Same name as the daughter of the Fortners\Nwho was killed in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's currently missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for sharing\Nsuch a painful story with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It matches perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the story Tenma told me\Nabout what's happened the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He came here\Nin his investigation of these cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He soon left\Nso he could assassinate Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Tenma was\Nat the library that day to carry out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,his assassination attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But then there was that fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I don't know if Tenma was even there,\Nlet alone Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Nina.\NStop going after Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's more than you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd agree\Nthat the police aren't much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to proceed slowly\Nand carefully in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, the truth will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry. We'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you rest here\Nfor the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-He was there.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was definitely there\Nat the library then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Kaiser rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've put roasted ham\Nand Gouda cheese on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Tenma's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's delicious.\N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Good food makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma always said that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's looking nice again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea. How about we take\Na trip when you're better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A trip to Asia might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a good change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you should really\Ntake it easy more often now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you've worked long\Nand hard enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A bridge…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Three frogs…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There were three frogs…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In his eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see hell…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see hell in the eyes\Nof a living human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something\NI want you to tell a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The man is waiting in Dresden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In Dresden? What should I tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want me to send that message\Nto the man waiting in Dresden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,she hated me, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She didn't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl, when you return from Dresden,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,will you stay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why, but I'm very scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But take your time. Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A town out of a fairytale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A fairytale town? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you feel\Nwhen you looked at this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me whatever comes to mind.\NAnything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Three frogs…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There were three frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There were three frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Three frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean they're in this picture book\Nthat made Johan faint?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no drawing of three frogs\Nanywhere in that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you see that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to hope that\NInspector Lunge of the BKA would help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.\NI think we should change our strategy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we bring evidence to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we should speak directly\Nwith his superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it should only be evidence\Nthat we've taken the time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to thoroughly research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But how much time should we take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The information we have on Johan now\Nis vague and there's far too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the man Johan worked for,\NSchuwald, has some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's still not taking visitors.\NWhat about his son, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He left for somewhere two days ago,\Nbut I can't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing concrete,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but some of the witnesses said\Nthat an Asian man helped them escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Tenma's fingerprints are found on\Nthe sniper rifle discovered at the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,no number of\Nwitness statements will save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How long should we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When the truth becomes clear\Nand the police take action,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma will…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, I understand very well how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost a close friend of mine,\NRichard, in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a bright future ahead of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Johan cut his future short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not giving up. Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Three frogs…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a town out of a fairy tale…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly. You can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Dr. Reichwein thank you\Nfor taking care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,DRESDEN\N(SAXONY)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Day three and still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to wait in the square\Nat the station, but this place is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll be able to meet\Nthe man you told me about, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Karl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who was attempting\Nto assassinate your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what the police told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you\Nfrom that building for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the police aren't tailing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. We're almost out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out.\NThe police will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Dresden.\NWait in the train station square.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My son Karl will bring you a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cedok Bridge.The Three Frogs"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My father also told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the monster\Nyou are chasing has a twin…"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The twins' mother is alive\Nand living in Prague.
